<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Matrículas</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        .icon {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-100">
<div class="container mx-auto mt-8 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Sistema de Matrículas</h1>
    <hr class="mb-4">

    <form action="/confirmacion" method="post">
        <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="curso" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Seleccione un curso:</label>
            <select class="form-control w-full border rounded-md p-2" id="curso" name="curso">
                <option value="Java">Java</option>
                <option value="PHP">PHP</option>
                <option value=".NET">.NET</option>
            </select>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Seleccione los módulos:</label>
            <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basico" name="basico" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md">
                    <label for="basico" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Básico</label>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="intermedio" name="intermedio" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md">
                    <label for="intermedio" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Intermedio</label>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="avanzado" name="avanzado" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md">
                    <label for="avanzado" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Avanzado</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Seleccione el medio de pago:</label>
            <div class="mt-2 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="tarjeta" name="medioPago" value="Tarjeta de crédito" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md">
                    <label for="basico" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Tarjeta de crédito</label>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="efectivo" name="medioPago" value="Pago en efectivo" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded-md">
                    <label for="intermedio" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Pago en efectivo</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-md">Siguiente</button>
    </form>

    <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Información de precios:</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Cada módulo del curso de Java está S/ 1200, los de PHP S/ 800 y los de .NET S/ 1500.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/java-coffee-cup-logo--v2.png" alt="Java Icon" class="icon">
            <span class="text-gray-700 mr-2">Java: S/ 1200</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/offices/40/000000/php-logo.png" alt="PHP Icon" class="icon">
            <span class="text-gray-700 mr-2">PHP: S/ 800</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center">
            <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/000000/dot-net.png" alt=".NET Icon" class="icon">
            <span class="text-gray-700 mr-2">.NET: S/ 1500</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
